## AI Assistant for job hunting

### 1. Setup
```
conda create -n hjh python=3.11
conda activate hjh
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -U python-jobspy
```

### 2. PDF profiling
Use a local LLM to parse profile
Resume must have the following sections : 
- Education
- Experience
- Projects
- Skills

### 3. Websites parsing
Use JobSpy to fetch jobs on linkedin, indeed and glassdoor

